==English==
===Verb===
'''[[not]] [[touch]] (something) [[with]] a [[ten]] [[foot]] [[pole]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[avoid]] something at all costs; to [[refuse]] to [[associate]] with something; signifies a strong [[aversion]].
#:''His father loved to sail, but he would '''not touch a boat with a ten foot pole'''.''

